    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Prerequisites:</strong> Dual Wielding sphere, Three-Sword Style, base attack bonus +16.</p>\n<p>When making a dual attack, you may expend your martial focus and forego any extra attacks that you might otherwise be able to make during your turn to treat each attack as an attack action. This means that each of the three attacks may be modified by feats such as Vital Strike, but cannot trigger any additional attacks, such as combat maneuvers added by talents when making an attack action normally.</p>\n",
